================================================================================
Third-party components
================================================================================

The mgi-mind binary distributed from GitHub Releases contains no third-party
runtime components: Qdrant, the ONNX Runtime and the embedding models are
fetched at runtime by `mgimind doctor --fix`.

The published Docker image, however, bakes those components into the image and
therefore redistributes them. Their notices follow.

