Rust crates
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
mgi-mind links a number of Rust crates, predominantly under the MIT and
Apache-2.0 licenses. The authoritative list for a given build is Cargo.lock;
`cargo license` or `cargo about` will render it with per-crate terms.

Notable direct dependencies include tokenizers and qdrant-client
(Apache-2.0), and ort, the Rust bindings for ONNX Runtime (MIT/Apache-2.0).
